#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
typedef long long typ;
int main()
{     
	typ start,end;
	typ a,b,c;
	while(1)
	{  int counter=0;
		a=1;
		b=2;
		cin>>start;
		cin>>end;
		if(start==0&&end==0)
		break;
	while(1)
	{
		
		c=a+b;
		a=b;
		b=c;
		if(c>=start&&c<=end)
	 counter++;
	   if(c>=end)
	   break;
	}
	cout<<counter<<endl;
   }
	return 0;
	
}
